>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="date">Being prepared by legal counsel</div>
  <p>The Privacy Policy for Lumecon and its family of products — Local Economic Impact, Tribal Economic Impact, and Global Economic Impact — are being prepared.</p>
  <p>This policy will cover data collection, use, sharing, analytics, retention, and your rights with respect to personal information provided through Lumecon's websites and services, including Cedar&trade;.</p>
  <p>Lumecon does not currently use third-party analytics or tracking on its websites.</p>
  <div class="note"><strong>Counsel:</strong> {site.counsel}<br>Contact: <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="note-link">{site.email}</a></div>
</LegalLayout>
